criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age over 18 years;

          -  Acute circulatory failure from any cause defined as low blood pressure (systolic blood
             pressure less than 90mmHg and/or mean arterial pressure less than 65mmHg) and/or
             marbling and mechanical ventilation;

          -  Affiliation with a social security scheme or entitled to it;

          -  Information and non-objection of the patient to participate in the research.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        -
